And to be honest, I don't like
the way Mossad investigates.

308
00:21:38,309 --> 00:21:40,075
We get the job done
though, no?

309
00:21:41,876 --> 00:21:43,509
Let's help each other.

310
00:21:43,542 --> 00:21:46,175
This is a Five Eyes site and
